    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s super dependable, looks great on the road, and has been well-loved. If you're looking for a reliable daily driver that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. It runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
