    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This driver-focused example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term mechanical reliability, the Vanos system has been professionally overhauled and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The suspension remains tight with updated bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative handling. While the aesthetics show honest road wear typical of a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain remains stout with linear power delivery and a crisp exhaust note. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
