    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014honest wear for a car of this age. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, with all electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, functioning perfectly. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has a complete service history, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement performed just 500 miles ago. The engine idles smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle for someone who appreciates quality and a well-documented history. Serious inquiries only; I am happy to provide the full maintenance log upon request.",
